description:
*An edited, illustrated and narrated playthrough of the game Dwarf Fortress*

 The fortress continues to explode in population as some strange new moods grip our dwarves! What will come of this??

--------------------

Thanks to everyone who helped out with this episode!

-Mrs K for her unending support and expert waxwork (she colors all the drawings. With crayons.)
 -Ivan Duch for making the theme and a lot of other songs for Spearcavern: https://ivanduch.com/

title: Spearcavern 16: Strange Moods..
